Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.80,0:02:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或是說蒼紫你還不敢正視現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想得到最強的證據\N來當隱身的蓑衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以死來逃避嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.47,0:02:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快找回往日那堅強的心\N喚醒失去的尊嚴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.87,0:02:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正是你覺醒的時候呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.58,0:02:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莊面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.25,0:02:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,式尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.88,0:02:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若 以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五十二話\N創造奇跡 葵屋的攻防戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們太天真了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.75,0:03:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是蒼紫還是安慈和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.68,0:03:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該下殺手時不肯下\N全是堆天真的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.95,0:03:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有空講廢話  還不快趕路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.09,0:03:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在你說話的時候\N葵屋的大家正…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先聲明 沒用的 這不是謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.66,0:03:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的同伴恐怕一個活口不剩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.13,0:03:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個女人就會胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.30,0:03:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒胡說  十本刀最後的一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.20,0:03:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密武器差不多該到葵屋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密武器？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.24,0:03:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰、禰彥、小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師父…你一定要趕上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.46,0:04:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是十本刀 飛翔的蝙也的戰術 飛空發破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.93,0:04:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管武術  到達多究極的地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.70,0:04:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭頂是人類的絕對死角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.10,0:04:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對于飛在上空的敵人\N要反擊根本是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.14,0:04:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「有辦法殺你就殺」\N這可是你說的大話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.28,0:04:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會如你所說的\N讓你生命的時間靜止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.70,0:04:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能死在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.07,0:04:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去的戰鬥\N一直是為了這一天呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.91,0:04:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你離開東京以後\N我沒有一天敢鬆懈練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.78,0:04:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我變得比你以為的\N還要強很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.02,0:05:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥  我不在時這媯鳩A留守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你留下來當防守的大將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.93,0:05:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我答應過劍心的\N要留下來成為防守的主力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.64,0:05:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.94,0:05:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好燙好燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.78,0:05:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 小心點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.65,0:05:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是我白雪般的肌膚\N燙傷了怎辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…那個瘋子人妖估且不論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.12,0:05:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連自己的手下你都不惜捲入\N你到底是什麼心態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,棋子隨時可以掉換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.24,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉由翅膀與爆風\N讓瘦骨如材的身體飛上天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.41,0:06:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天上自由自在攻擊\N這樣下去 禰彥是沒勝算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.08,0:06:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你若是轉過身去\N我馬上把你砍成兩半哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.45,0:06:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去助陣是沒用的\N反正到最後一樣是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.36,0:06:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說誰呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.06,0:06:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要攻我就兩個人同時上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.47,0:06:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得我給你們二比一的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.41,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 不只頭上是死角\N他還對我的行動瞭若指掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制空權在他手上\N我根本就無計施展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.82,0:06:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.02,0:06:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該還是有辦法的\N應該有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.46,0:06:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 如果我可以跳得比他更高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.70,0:06:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那蝙蝠傢伙的態度看來\N一定沒有人飛得比他更高過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.04,0:07:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 來自上方的攻擊\N或許是反敗為勝的關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.91,0:07:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…怎樣才能比他高呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換成劍心的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.28,0:07:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也許能配合爆風\N飛得比那傢伙更高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.39,0:07:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是有那翅膀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 有代替翅膀的東西的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 彈藥差不多完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次就讓你結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.50,0:07:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了 禰彥到堶崤N快逃進葵屋堶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.04,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃？開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.08,0:07:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要遵守與劍心的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不堪一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.19,0:07:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我的飛空發破絕招前\N沒有人是我的敵手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.49,0:08:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下就用剩下的彈藥\N早點把他們通通殺光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.67,0:08:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我比你更高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.37,0:08:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小鬼 竟然以門板當翅膀\N跳得比我更高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.08,0:08:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流  神龍不見尾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍槌閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用看的就會了！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了平日的練習之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.49,0:08:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加上緋村與強敵交手時\N在旁觀戰的心得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.10,0:08:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然進步了兩倍 不 三倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我不知不覺中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.51,0:08:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他連劍心的絕招\N龍槌閃都會模仿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.15,0:08:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這孩子…還會越來越強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.72,0:09:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要象劍心那樣果然很難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧 怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蝙也敗給一個小鬼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.94,0:09:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 剩下還有兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來就一口氣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.11,0:09:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打…倒…他們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.12,0:09:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正到最後你們都會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.41,0:09:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的\N禰彥不會那麼簡單就死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是你要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.02,0:10:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次換我們戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.29,0:10:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你跟那位小丫頭不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.16,0:10:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小丫頭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我與她沒多少差別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.36,0:10:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是像這樣綁蝴蝶結\N身著道服的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.44,0:10:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有著不分男女\N身為一位劍士的覺悟罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.61,0:10:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這方面看來\N我與你是差不多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 也許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是實力就差多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十本刀之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.15,0:10:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大鐮刀的鐮足\N與一位劍士的差別是很大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.96,0:10:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 小操 看他的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.79,0:10:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大鐮刀怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.63,0:10:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個看來最輕也有八貫重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.43,0:10:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要分類的話 毫無疑問\N屬於超重武器之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.00,0:10:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超重武器的殺傷力大\N但是揮空時破綻也大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.27,0:11:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我們要瞄準的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.48,0:11:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當誘餌 誘使他揮空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.15,0:11:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操你趁那機會\N一口氣攻擊他的要害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.72,0:11:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 放馬過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你說我們也會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.94,0:11:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.31,0:11:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.27,0:12:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想對準超重武器的弱點進攻\N這個著眼點是不錯啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.04,0:12:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惜那招對我沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.48,0:12:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我\N被稱為使用大鐮刀的鐮足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.85,0:12:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我使用的武器是 大鎖鐮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.79,0:12:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個真髓卻在於\N鐮刀與鎖鏈的波狀攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.50,0:12:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使出來了  鐮刀大人必殺絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂弁天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.51,0:12:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂弁天斬斷所有接觸到的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.61,0:12:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這攻防一體的絕招\N你是破不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.23,0:12:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.86,0:13:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作一點 小操 小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.36,0:14:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.84,0:14:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這聲音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊信守約定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.44,0:14:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫大人會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.16,0:14:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 原來你擔心我\N回來看我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.17,0:14:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 肋骨斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣無法作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.18,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…我不能這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事也沒做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.02,0:15:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就倒下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.99,0:15:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那絕招面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很難打中他的要害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能打中的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.56,0:15:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄準吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貫殺飛飛鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.20,0:15:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞武器？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.91,0:15:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太小看他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.14,0:15:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還以為跟第一擊一樣\N想瞄準我的要害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.08,0:15:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於大鎖鐮的妨礙\N無法瞄準要害的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就只好先破壞大鎖鐮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但光靠我的尺鏢威力還是不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.59,0:15:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠阿薰的木刀也沒有辦法斬斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.26,0:15:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就讓飛鏢當椿\N破壞棍 子就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想得好 好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得蒼紫大人要回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.00,0:15:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然不能再給般若添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.77,0:16:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 這樣的形勢逆轉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.44,0:16:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 一口氣打垮他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.32,0:16:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐮足先生這樣你還不肯撤走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您失去了大鎖鐮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.19,0:16:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的你   沒有打贏的要素了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再鬥爭下去   一點意義也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.90,0:16:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑死人了\N說我沒有打贏的要素？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點你們也一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.71,0:16:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 神谷活心流的主旨\N是使人活下去的活人劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.08,0:16:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其秘訣不是殺死對方\N而是要制住對方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.28,0:16:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就算沒有刀刃\N光是劍柄 也足可戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.52,0:16:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來也不是虛張聲勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.76,0:16:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.43,0:16:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也預備了鐮刀折斷時的絕招呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect, 面對阿薰…他終於認真起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.57,0:17:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼\N我隨時都是很認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.11,0:17:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.24,0:17:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有相當的覺悟\N是沒辦法當人妖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.95,0:17:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論身為男人 或是 女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.65,0:17:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都是無法成為志志雄大人\N的最愛的半吊子人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.25,0:17:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以至少要完美地達成\N他給我的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.03,0:17:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我將所有的愛都灌注進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.73,0:17:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為志志雄大人的力量\N就是我的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.16,0:17:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這塈甯O絕不退讓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.74,0:17:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本條流大鎖鏈鐮術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.17,0:17:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect, 弁天獨樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.86,0:18:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我也不能退讓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.93,0:18:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟劍心約好\N大家一起回東京的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.14,0:18:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分出勝負了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.88,0:18:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託 請你們撤退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法行動的傷患
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.48,0:18:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連你在內我們都會負責治療的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.02,0:18:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過   執行任務是我的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.63,0:18:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這出醜的模樣\N我絕不能讓志志雄大人看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小丫頭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.41,0:18:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我討厭這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.78,0:18:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我不懂人妖的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.29,0:19:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但想幫助喜歡的人的心\N我非常瞭解呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.36,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.91,0:19:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能   在蝙也大人之後\N連鐮足大人也輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.24,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect, 十本刀之中\N兩個人被 女人小孩打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.25,0:19:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怕 我們還有肉不倒翁\N不 是還有夷腕坊大人戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.76,0:19:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夷腕坊大人   夷腕坊大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.40,0:19:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他太傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.59,0:20:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才他的腦袋\N是不是轉了360度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.13,0:20:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是你眼睛看錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.18,0:20:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.38,0:20:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們目的達成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.85,0:20:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.99,0:20:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們獲勝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有東西…在靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.27,0:21:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某種巨大無比的東西是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.06,0:21:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 鐮足被打敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.06,0:21:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.45,0:22:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子我們兩個人\N可以獨佔獵物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.96,0:22:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說是吧 不二

